						<summary>

						<p>This inscription registers the gift of 10 sheep which is neither died nor aged for burning lamps in the temple of Kiḍanda perumāḷ by Suramittap-Perumaṉṟāḍi, son of Irukaṇṇaṉ residing at Kiḻvaḻi Toṇḍur in Śiṅgapura nāḍu. </p>						

